nt-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">We will assist our teachers in obtaining a Z-visa/Foreign Expert Certificate/Residence permit. Our school has the certificates that allow us to hire foreigners legally. If the teacher does not have a Z-visa yet, he/she should visit their home country to apply.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\" />\r\n<strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">Full time/part time:</strong><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">Our school only has full time options, since we are not allowed to hire foreigners who do not hold a work visa or hold their work visa elsewhere.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\" />\r\n<strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">Age:&nbsp;</strong><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6)