28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">- Vocational allowance;</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">Working hours: 20 teaching hours per week. One teaching hour is 45 minutes.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\" />\r\n<strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">Housing</strong><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">Housing for Foreign Teachers is free of charge. Utilities are paid by the Foreign Teacher. The housing is furnished according to western style. All apartments are equipped with air conditioner, washing machine, TV, induction plate for cooking and microwave.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\" />\r\n<a style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\"><img alt=\"华广外教招聘\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://communi.chenyimin.cn/uploadfile/2017/0411/20170411050415861.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 600px;\" /></a>',0,'',0,10000,'',0,'','','|0',1),(34,'<a style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\"><img alt=\"华广外教守则\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://communi.chenyimin.cn/uploadfile/2017/0411/20170411050547526.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 600px;\" /></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">See also from&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">The</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">Foreign Teachers&rsquo; Guide</strong><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\" />\r\n<strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">Chapter 11:Code of Conduct</strong><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">All Foreign Teachers must abide by the laws of China concerning residence, work, wages, benefits and travel of foreigners when entering, staying, leaving and passing through the territory of China.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\" />\r\n<strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">11.1 Student relationships</strong>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none;\">Foreign Teachers have to behave professionally and keep professional distance from the students. This means dating and physical contact are not allowed between the teachers and students.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none;\">Students are not allowed in the teacher&#39;s housings.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none;\">We expect our Foreign Teachers to behave professionally and keep a professional relationship with the students. Every complaint of harassment will be investigated and taken seriously by the college.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none;\">The students have a curfew on every school night which is set at 23:00. Students are responsible for observing this curfew. If they do not observe the curfew because they were &ldquo;out&rdquo; with a Foreign Teacher, then the Foreign Teacher is also partially responsible. So please encourage them to return home in time.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">11.2 Representatives</strong><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">Our Foreign Teachers are representatives of our college. This involves the following:</span>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none;\">No heavy drinking of alcohol and/or smoking in sight of the students.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none;\">Dress appropriately: Foreign Teacher&#39;s clothing should be clean, unwrinkled, in good repair and modest. Please cover your shoulders, knees and in between. For shoes, make sure your toes and heel is covered.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none;\">Do not wear any hats or piercings. If you have any tattoos, make sure they are covered before class, during class and after class.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none;\">Do not use inappropriate or obscene language with students, staff, colleagues or neighbors.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none;\">Behave in a respectable manner both in and out of the classroom and not engage in any activities that might damage the reputation of Guangzhou College.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none;\">Foreign Teachers are encouraged to spend their free time on campus and be engaged in activities with the students.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none;\">Foreign Teachers are also encouraged to promote our college:\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none;\">Writing professional articles or books and get published in the name of the school.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none;\">Every semester Guangzhou College will need more Foreign Teachers, you can help you friends/family getting a job here, if you think they are suitable for teaching here.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none;\">Take pictures of events and take part in events.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none;\">Take part in promotional videos or other merchandise.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">11.3 Teaching rules</strong><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">These are the rules for the Foreign Teachers for their classroom-teaching and scheduling.</span>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none;\">Please make sure you are prepared for every class and you arrive 5-10 minutes in advance, to prepare the classroom and make seating arrangements (if necessary). Do not dismiss the class earlier than the scheduled time.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none;\">Do not carry out any religious propaganda or religious activities with the students or Chinese people.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none;\">Please be flexible with the scheduling of classes for each semester, this means working up to 20 classroom teaching hours and 2 hours of English Corner a week. Classes may be assigned to you at any given point of the semester if you are not teaching up to 20 hours a week. The schedule is not set at the beginning of the semester, since the IECC might have to change it, due to events beyond control.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>11.4 Teamwork</strong><br />\r\nThe Foreign Teachers on our campus are considered to be a team. Even though you might not be close to other fellow Foreign Teachers, please realize that the Foreign Teachers are seen as one collective. If you feel other Foreign Teachers are behaving in an irresponsible manner, it is not only their own reputation they might be damaging, but possibly yours as well.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>Chapter 12: Teaching regulations</strong><br />\r\nThe following teaching regulations involve the students and these regulations need to be communicated to the students on every first class of the semester. If necessary the teacher can repeat this every class.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>12.1 Attendance</strong><br />\r\nAll students in the college need to be graded after every course. The attendance is part of their grade. If a student is absent more than 10-20% of the course, lowering their grade is necessary. If a student is absent more than 30% of the course, they will have to fail the course.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nEvery teacher in the college is obligated to take attendance at the beginning of the class and has to hand over the attendance administration at the end of the semester.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nIf a student can provide an official absence slip, their absence can be ignored.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>12.2 Arriving late for class</strong><br />\r\nIf a student arrives more than 5 minutes late for class, their attendance should not be taken.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>12.3 Grading</strong><br />\r\nA student grade involves their attendance and performance. It can also include the student attitude. If a student misbehaves in the classroom or does not follow up on instructions, it can affect their grade. It is up to the teacher to decide this, but the teacher should motivate this in a written letter.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n',0,'',0,10000,'',0,'','','|0',1),(35,'<strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">外教晚宴Dinners</strong><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">Our Foreign Teachers are very much appreciated in our college. To show our gratitude and getting familiar with our teachers, we invite our teachers at least once per semester for dinner.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">学校领导十分关系外教的在校生活。每学期至少邀请外教参加一次晚宴，以表达对外教的关怀。</span><a style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\"><img alt=\"外教活动Foreign Teachers Activities\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://communi.chenyimin.cn/uploadfile/2017/0411/20170411050653547.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 600px;\" /></a><a style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\"><img alt=\"外教活动Foreign Teachers Activities\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://communi.chenyimin.cn/uploadfile/2017/0411/20170411050653366.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 600px;\" /></a><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\" />\r\n<strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">英语角English corner</strong><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">Every Thursday evening the Foreign Teachers and English Association organize English Corner, where Foreign Teachers host different activities like: English resume and application letter checking, extra oral English, discussion groups, English karaoke, English cinema.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">每周四晚，外教和英语协会将举办英语角活动，活动上，外教们不仅热心帮助学生修改英文简历和推荐信，引导学生参加主题讨论，还有精彩的英文K歌和观看英文电影等节目。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\" />\r\n<strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">学生社团Student unions</strong><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">All Foreign Teachers are invited to join in the student unions for activities. We have teachers joining in the soccer team and Kung-Fu club. This is encouraged by Guangzhou College to establish a better relationship with the students.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.8px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\">所有外教都受邀参加学生社团组织，例如足球队和功夫俱乐部。学校十分重视在校师生关系。</span>',0,'',0,10000,'',0,'','','|0',1),(44,'',0,'',0,10000,'',0,'','{\"0\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/communi.chenyimin.cn\\/uploadfile\\/2017\\/0418\\/20170418041414419.png\",\"alt\":\"20170418041414419\"}}','|0',1),(46,'',0,'',0,10000,'',0,'','{\"0\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/communi.chenyimin.cn\\/uploadfile\\/2017\\/0418\\/20170